ss=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mjf1665702682527.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mjf1665702682527.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mjf1665702682527.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mjf1665702682527\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__ugetames_403218\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get the complete, unfiltered asynchronous message from the input queue.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__topic_d120137e1_d120138e1_d120139e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mjf1665702682527_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__codeblock_oyn_cvz_zvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">short ugetames (unsigned char* message)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__topic_d85482e1_d85483e1_d85484e1_d85485e1_d85486e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d154741e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__parml_qy2_2vz_zvb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">message</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Asynchronous message data. This buffer must be large enough to hold the largest\n                  expected message. (Output)</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__topic_d85487e1_d85488e1_d85489e1_d85490e1_d85491e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d154741e80\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__p_d120152e1_d120153e1_d120154e1\">The length of the message or -1 if there is no message. -1 can occur in the following circumstances:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__li_d45167e1_d45168e1_d45169e1\">A procedure invokes <span class=\"keyword apiname\">ugetames</span>\n               when there is no asynchronous message being processed.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__li_d45170e1_d45171e1_d45172e1\">No text was supplied with the message.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__li_d45173e1_d45174e1_d45175e1\">The receiveMessage trigger requests other user\n               input (for example, with an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">askmess</span> instruction) before activating\n               the 3GL procedure containing <span class=\"keyword apiname\">ugetames</span>.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__li_d45176e1_d45177e1_d45178e1\">The application is in ProcScript debug mode\n               before <span class=\"keyword apiname\">ugetames</span>.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__topic_d85492e1_d85493e1_d85494e1_d85495e1_d85496e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d154741e116\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__topic_d85497e1_d85498e1_d85499e1_d85500e1_d85501e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d154741e129\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__p_d120164e1_d120165e1_d120166e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ugetames</code> copies the complete data\n            of an asynchronous message into the specified buffer. This function is primarily useful\n            when the message contains non-printable ASCII characters which are stripped out when\n            moved to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"mjf1665702682527__note_N1009A_N10086_N10016_N10001\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> You should use\n               <span class=\"keyword apiname\">ugetames</span> only in a 3GL routine that was called from the\n            receiveMessage trigger.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qcz1665702682393.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uputames</a><p>Put an asynchronous message in the input queue of the calling application.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529945\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529945\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ugetames Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get the complete, unfiltered asynchronous message from the input queue. Explain this code short ugetames (unsigned char* message) Copy Parameters message Asynchronous message data. This buffer must be large enough to hold the largest expected message. (Output) Return Values The length of the message or -1 if there is no message. -1 can occur in the following circumstances: A procedure invokes ugetames when there is no asynchronous message being processed. No text was supplied with the message. The receiveMessage trigger requests other user input (for example, with an askmess instruction) before activating the 3GL procedure containing ugetames . The application is in ProcScript debug mode before ugetames . Use Library: yrtl Description ugetames copies the complete data of an asynchronous message into the specified buffer. This function is primarily useful when the message contains non-printable ASCII characters which are stripped out when moved to $result . Note: You should use ugetames only in a 3GL routine that was called from the receiveMessage trigger. Related Links uputames Put an asynchronous message in the input queue of the calling application. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}